632
00:40:33,355 --> 00:40:34,365
No, wait.

633
00:40:34,524 --> 00:40:35,534
Here.

634
00:40:36,325 --> 00:40:37,335
Use reusable paper.

635
00:40:41,264 --> 00:40:43,094
