640
00:40:51,504 --> 00:40:53,596
Gyeong Hyeon, if this becomes a huge hit,

641
00:40:54,245 --> 00:40:55,588
I'll give you some shares.

642
00:40:58,684 --> 00:41:00,058
Write up a contract and sign it.

643
00:41:00,914 --> 00:41:04,662
