674
00:42:34,875 --> 00:42:36,530
Please.

675
00:42:38,985 --> 00:42:40,055
Ms. Son.

676
00:42:40,585 --> 00:42:42,883
If you fail to pass this year,

677
00:42:42,884 --> 00:42:45,248
